    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>torn ciabatta[s] </strong>to a baking tray with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 5 min or until golden and crisp – these are your <strong>croutons</strong></p>",
