    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s] </strong>in half lengthways, around the stone[s]</p><p>Remove the stone[s] using a spoon, then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh</strong> and dice roughly</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
