    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your<strong> tomato[es]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Chop your<strong> basil</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
