    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, drain your <strong>king prawns</strong>, then add them to the pan with the <strong>remaining sliced garlic </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until cooked through</p><p>Once cooked, squeeze in the juice<strong> </strong>of the <strong>remaining lemon </strong>– these are your <strong>lemony king prawns</strong></p>",
